      <section id="id4423445"><title>Gearbox, clutch, and bellhousing</title><para id="id4468091">As with the S2 and S3 Seven, the Ford Mark 2 Cortina GT/Corsair 2000E gearbox was employed. More correctly known as the 2821E, it is a semi-close ratio 4-speed all synchromesh gearbox (<link target-id=" id3888067"/>), with synchromesh on all forward gears. Since it was also used in the Lotus Elan it meant a commonality of supply for Lotus Cars and Lotus Components. </para>

