    <section id="id4401487"><title>Wheels and tires</title><para id="id1169759143817">The S4 Seven was provided standard with 5 <sup>1</sup>/<sub>2</sub>" x 13" pressed steel 'bolt-on' rims with chromium plated hub-caps (<link target-id="id4348221"/>). As an upgrade 5<sup>1</sup>/<sub>2</sub>" x 13" light alloy 'bolt-on' Brand Lotus rims were available at extra cost (<link target-id="id1169745835415"/>). Both wheels were supplied with either 165 x 13” Dunlop SP Sport or Goodyear G800 radial tires as standard.</para>


